without going into any sort of strenuous exercises.

100
00:06:47,384 --> 00:06:50,886
But, when we talk of Kalki we have to remember,

101
00:06:51,013 --> 00:06:54,051
that between getting our realization

102
00:06:54,179 --> 00:06:58,859
and entering into the Kingdom of God, we can falter very much.

103
00:07:00,572 --> 00:07:03,542
This is called as ‘Yoga bhrashta sthiti’.

104
00:07:04,097 --> 00:07:07,270
People take to yoga, they come into yoga,

105
00:07:07,373 --> 00:07:11,556
and are then enchanted still by their pravrutis
(tendencies).

106
00:07:11,821 --> 00:07:15,455
For example an ego oriented man or a money oriented man

107
00:07:15,669 --> 00:07:17,734
or a man who wants to dominate,

108
00:07:17,853 --> 00:07:21,830
can form a group of people whom he would dominate

109
00:07:22,040 --> 00:07:23,670
by his ideas and

110
00:07:23,783 --> 00:07:27,034
can go in for a fall and the rest of them will also go down.

111
00:07:27,136 --> 00:07:28,463
In Sahaja Yoga itself.

112
00:07:28,542 --> 00:07:30,741
This has been happening in Bombay, very, very

113
