often, it's a very very common thing that has been going on.

114
00:07:34,230 --> 00:07:37,055
But this is called as ‘Yogabhrashtata’,

115
00:07:37,281 --> 00:07:39,526
where a person falls from his yoga,

116
00:07:39,647 --> 00:07:41,526
he comes down on his yoga,

117
00:07:41,593 --> 00:07:43,929
because Sahaja Yoga gives you all the freedom,

118
00:07:44,032 --> 00:07:46,070
whether to fall or to come up.

119
00:07:46,189 --> 00:07:48,349
But if you go to any other guru,

120
00:07:48,474 --> 00:07:52,135
doing any other sort of yoga in which purification takes place,

121
00:07:52,214 --> 00:07:55,942
and where people are trained and disciplined from very childhood,

122
00:07:56,079 --> 00:07:58,130
 in those yogas a guru

