00:07:58,346 --> 00:08:00,874
will somehow or other see that you are injured

124
00:08:00,956 --> 00:08:03,212
or you are hurt so badly that you have no

125
00:08:03,306 --> 00:08:05,205
connections with anybody else,

126
00:08:05,365 --> 00:08:08,913
 like an operation. They take out that personality and throw him out.

127
00:08:09,117 --> 00:08:11,621
But here it is left to your freedom

128
00:08:11,734 --> 00:08:15,804
to understand that, you have to keep to the mains,

129
00:08:16,302 --> 00:08:19,048
you have to keep to the group,

130
00:08:19,196 --> 00:08:24,434
you have to keep to the whole, and not to one person here and there

131
00:08:24,581 --> 00:08:28,298
who is trying to overpower the rest of you.

132
00:08:29,009 --> 00:08:31,947
In Sahaja Yoga anybody who tries to come up too much

133
00:08:32,073 --> 00:08:34,533
comes down, because in nature you have seen,

134
00:08:34,657 --> 00:08:37,152
nothing grows out of bounds.

135
00:08:37,443 --> 00:08:40,353
Like human beings are of a certain height,

136
00:08:40,604 --> 00:08:43,120
the trees are of certain heights,

137
00:08:43,409 --> 00:08:45,456
everything is controlled.

138
00:08:45,844 --> 00:08:48,585
You cannot try to show off in Sahaja Yoga,

139
00:08:48,688 --> 00:08:51,183
neither you should try to make a different

140
00:08:51,330 --> 00:08:54,436
group or a different type of some special thing.

141
00:08:54,720 --> 00:08:57,204
Specially I have seen in Sahaja Yoga there are people

142
00:08:57,284 --> 00:08:59,986
