00:11:43,317 --> 00:11:45,518
Not only those who are Sahaja Yogis,

203
00:11:45,598 --> 00:11:49,781
but this I am telling to the whole world today, that - Be careful!

204
00:11:49,910 --> 00:11:51,880
Do not try to harm others.

